Using:
Copy terrain.png to bin/ directory.  This test program will preview how each
block will look with this skin, using libmc--c.

Controls:
Zoom        Mouse-wheel scroll, PageUp, PageDown
Move        Left-click drag, arrow keys, WASD
Turn        Right-click drag, Home, End
Respawn     Middle-click
Tree color  R, G, B

Thanks to the following people for testing:
vLK
